<h2 id="mentoring-and-evaluation-boards">Mentoring and evaluation boards</h2>

<p>From my Ph.D. project, an official funding application and some additional research came to life, and I ended up helping master and undergraduate students in their investigations.</p>

<p>Also, I took part in evaluation boards of master and undergrad. theses, as well as other judgment committees.</p>

